      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Your &quot;indexOf&quot; example should use &gt;= 0, not &gt; 0, since 0 is valid if the substring occurs at the beginning of the string.  (Doesn&#39;t in your example, but could in other cases.)  Added this response since people are obviously still searching and finding this answer."
